      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just the grief. it's like... what's even the point of doing anything else? i go through the motions, i eat, i sleep, i work, but it's all so hollow. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. everything just feels pointless now.",
